|Args| value|

| source_prompt | “An astronaut riding a horse” |

安装 cuda11.7 的develop版paddle
```sh

```

```python
import paddle
import time

paddle.set_device('gpu:7')
from ppdiffusers import StableDiffusionPipeline

height = 1024
width = 1024
fp16 = True
enable_xformers_memory_efficient_attention = True
paddle_dtype = paddle.float16 if fp16 else paddle.float32

pipe = StableDiffusionPipeline.from_pretrained("runwayml/stable-diffusion-v1-5", safety_checker=None, paddle_dtype=paddle_dtype)
prompt = "a portrait of shiba inu with a red cap growing on its head. intricate. lifelike. soft light. sony a 7 r iv 5 5 mm. cinematic post - processing "

if enable_xformers_memory_efficient_attention:
    pipe.enable_xformers_memory_efficient_attention()
    png = "enable-memory-efficient-attention.png"
else:
    pipe.disable_xformers_memory_efficient_attention()
    png = "disable-memory-efficient-attention.png"

# warmup
with paddle.amp.auto_cast(fp16, level='O2'):
    image = pipe(prompt, guidance_scale=7.5, height=512, width=512, num_inference_steps=10).images[0]

a1 = time.time()
with paddle.amp.auto_cast(fp16, level='O2'):
    paddle.seed(42)
    image = pipe(prompt, guidance_scale=7.5, height=height, width=width, num_inference_steps=100).images[0]
b1 = time.time()
image.save(png)
print(b1-a1)
```

```python
# ppdiffusers == 0.11.0
from ppdiffusers import CycleDiffusionPipeline, DDIMScheduler
from ppdiffusers.utils import load_image
import paddle
init_image = load_image("https://paddlenlp.bj.bcebos.com/models/community/CompVis/data/black_colored_car.png")
init_image = init_image.resize((512, 512))

model_id = "CompVis/stable-diffusion-v1-4"
pipe = CycleDiffusionPipeline.from_pretrained(model_id, safety_checker=None, requires_safety_checker=False)
pipe.scheduler = DDIMScheduler.from_config(pipe.scheduler.config)

source_prompt = "A black colored car"
prompt = "A blue colored car"

generator = paddle.Generator().manual_seed(0)
output = pipe(
    prompt=prompt,
    source_prompt=source_prompt,
    image=init_image,
    num_inference_steps=100,
    eta=0.1,
    strength=0.85,
    guidance_scale=3,
    source_guidance_scale=1,
    generator=generator,
    output_type="pil",
).images

output[0].save("demo.png")
```
